This is an unofficial soundtrack (UST) for My Litte Pony: Equestria Girls. All
tracks were ripped directly from the DVD disc. Songs were trimmed by hand in
Audacity, and fade-in/out effects were added where needed.

Note: The song "This Is Our Big Night" was split into two parts in the movie.
Those parts are included separately, and also (crudely) joined together as a
bonus track.

Enjoy!
